{
  "stem": "23410.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because-- and if it's something unpleasant, something bad, I will show you, I am Leon Wells, so they got the bad-- the wrong name.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because I am a good worker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm everyday, I did not miss one day of work, since September or October, I don't even remember.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they came on Saturday, and they took us all by truck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They called out the name, and I came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I said, I am Wells.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Weliczker.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went there, and they took me to Lvov.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To the center. to the headquarters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came to the headquarters, And they all took us to the Janowska camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to backtrack for one moment before we go on with Janowska.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In this time, up to 1942, were you able to be practicing Jews?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were you able to go for services?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How restricted was that part of your life?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we did not go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not think about going to services.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did not go out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember, it was the Yom Kippur before, in '41.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had in the shtiebel, they got together a few people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it wasn't anything of any importance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't great danger, but nobody thought in terms of greater danger or great-- you-- you do certain things without even thinking.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But maybe because I was young, maybe they thought, or not, I cannot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I myself was, this is how it is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is how it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The whole idea was that the people of my father's age, being from World War I, knew that if England, France, and Russia's going to war with Germany, the war will be over in no time.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
